OL,3,CWater company fined #350,000 after
OL,4,Cpumping station incident and sewage
OL,5,Cdischarge
OL,7,FYorkshire Water has been fined
OL,8,F#350,000 after one of its sewage
OL,9,Fpumping stations polluted a York
OL,10,Fwatercourse.
OL,12,FThe company pleaded guilty to two
OL,13,Foffences - one of illegally polluting
OL,14,FFoss Dyke with sewage, and another in
OL,15,Frelation to failing to maintain a pump
OL,16,Fat the pumping station.
OL,18,FYork Magistrates Court heard how
OL,19,FYorkshire Water was aware Fossbridge
OL,20,FSewage Pumping Station's backup pump
OL,21,Fhad not been working for five months.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
