OL,3,CWater company fined #350,000 after
OL,4,Cpumping station incident and sewage
OL,5,Cdischarge
OL,7,FIt had failed to repair it, despite
OL,8,Fthe issue having been noted repeatedly
OL,9,Fduring regular maintenance checks -
OL,10,Fand should have been fixed within 24
OL,11,Fhours.
OL,13,FSensors enable Yorkshire Water to
OL,14,Fmonitor the station's performance
OL,15,Fincluding power, pump condition,
OL,16,Flevels and the operation of the
OL,17,Femergency overflow.
OL,19,FWhat happened between 2017 and 2018?
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
