OL,3,CWater company fined #350,000 after
OL,4,Cpumping station incident and sewage
OL,5,Cdischarge
OL,7,FOn 5 October 2017, Yorkshire Water
OL,8,Fnoted the inlet pipe feeding the
OL,9,Fbackup pump was blocked - meaning the
OL,10,Fpump could not operate.
OL,12,FA job was raised several times to fix
OL,13,Fthe blockage, but it was never done.
OL,15,FYorkshire Water claimed the repair of
OL,16,Fthe backup pump was to be done by an
OL,17,Fexternal contractor, but had "got lost
OL,18,Fin the ether".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
