OL,3,CWater company fined #350,000 after
OL,4,Cpumping station incident and sewage
OL,5,Cdischarge
OL,7,FThe company stopped the discharge and
OL,8,Farranged for tankers to transport the
OL,9,Fsewage away from the pumping station
OL,10,Fwhile it was repaired. Reports suggest
OL,11,Fthe pumping station had been
OL,12,Fdischarging intermittently into the
OL,13,Fwatercourse on 12 March 2018.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
