OL,3,CWater company fined #350,000 after
OL,4,Cpumping station incident and sewage
OL,5,Cdischarge
OL,7,FOver the following days, two further
OL,8,Fdischarges took place at the pumping
OL,9,Fstation, one because only one tanker
OL,10,Fwas being used to transport sewage
OL,11,Ffrom the pumping station and it had
OL,12,Fnot been able to keep up with the
OL,13,Fflow, and another after the main pump
OL,14,Fblocked again.
OL,16,FWater samples showed high ammonia
OL,17,Flevels in the watercourse.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
