OL,3,CWater company fined #350,000 after
OL,4,Cpumping station incident and sewage
OL,5,Cdischarge
OL,7,FMartin Christmas, Area Environment
OL,8,FManager for the Environment Agency in
OL,9,FYorkshire, said: "Water companies have
OL,10,Fa responsibility to ensure their
OL,11,Fassets are maintained and in working
OL,12,Forder to protect the environment.
OL,14,F"Yorkshire Water failed to take action
OL,15,Fdespite being aware of the risks posed
OL,16,Fby one of its pumps being out of
OL,17,Faction, which led to a sewage spill.
OL,19,F"We expect full compliance and are
OL,20,Fcommitted to taking robust enforcement
OL,21,Faction where we see serious breaches.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
